    "desc": "2+ monsters with different names<br />If this card is Link Summoned: You can discard 1 card, then target 1 card on the field; shuffle it into the Deck, then, if this card was co-linked when this effect was activated, you can draw 1 card. You can only use this effect of \"Knightmare Unicorn\" once per turn. While any co-linked \"Knightmare\" monsters are on the field, for your normal draw in your Draw Phase, draw 1 card for each different card name among those co-linked \"Knightmare\" monsters, instead of drawing just 1 card.",
